+denial, protected file-handle export denial, protected directory delete and
+rename denial, direct and recursive deny-find
+directory-entry hiding, recursive tree children including
+nested attr, xattr, access-probe, stat, list, and find changes, and append-only rewrite and shared writable mapping paths are denied while unmatched files,
