+# SPDX-License-Identifier: GPL-2.0-only
+#
+# Product image read-only mount list for hdn-rofs-apply.
+#
+# Entries may be:
+#   required PATH   fail image sealing if PATH cannot be sealed read-only
+#   optional PATH   seal PATH only when it is a mounted filesystem
+#   PATH            compatibility alias for required PATH
+#
+# Keep mutable state such as /var, /home, /run, /tmp, and package-manager
+# working directories out of this list unless the image design provides an
+# overlay or a ROFS_RELAX updater/recovery profile.
+
+required /usr
+optional /boot
+optional /boot/efi
+optional /opt
+optional /usr/local
+optional /var/lib/flatpak
+optional /var/lib/snapd
